title: Prodigy Neck Frill Power Suit for Women – Jacket and Pant Set
body_html: Introducing Prodigy, a luxurious yet thought-provoking jacket with neck frill detailing and crepe fabric that moves with your body. This exquisitely crafted piece is perfect to elevate your look for any occasion. Sharp enough for a big day at work, it features an asymmetrical frill and is designed to feel as elegant as it is irreverent. A transitional must-have, pair with the matching navy Catalyst dress pants – this is power suit for women styling, done right.

title: Eternal Tweed Power Suit for Women – Jacket with White Pant Set
body_html:
Crafted from soft tweed, the new Eternal jacket is here to infuse the everyday with a charming touch. The formal double-breasted design is offset by a playful pink and gold hue, making it the perfect power suit for women—suited for both the office and after-work events. Sharp tailoring and deep pockets speak to Point of View genesis, while meticulously placed seams create a modern silhouette. The subtle elastic on the sleeve adds practicality for when you need to roll up your sleeves.
We’re styling ours with the Forever white trousers separates for an elegant look.
